<text x="36.83" y="-31.75" size="1.778" layer="97">F1: Fuse 1 [A]
*Interrupting Rating: 50 [A] at 32 [VDC]</text>
<text x="175.26" y="-34.29" size="1.778" layer="97" align="bottom-center">*Either +5V or +3.3V allows signaling
between USB host and V003.</text>
<text x="210.82" y="-167.64" size="2.7432" layer="94" font="vector">CH32V006</text>
<text x="180.34" y="-6.096" size="1.778" layer="97" align="bottom-center">System Voltage Selection</text>
<text x="220.98" y="-34.29" size="1.778" layer="97" align="bottom-center">*Either VCC or +5V allows signaling
between V003 and V006.</text>
<wire x1="191.77" y1="-17.78" x2="196.85" y2="-17.78" width="0.1524" layer="97" style="shortdash"/>
