<text x="39.37" y="-125.476" size="1.778" layer="97">FT: 5V tolerant</text>
<text x="198.12" y="-40.64" size="1.778" layer="97" align="bottom-center">*Never output voltage from the CH32V006 to the pins that are not 5V tolerant,
when the system voltage is +3.3V and the CH32V006 voltage is +5V.</text>
