https://www.usb.org/document-library/usb-20-specification</text>
<text x="10.16" y="-144.78" size="1.778" layer="97" align="top-left">4.11.3.2.5 Example of Voltage on Source CC Pins – Rp @ 3.3 V
        Table 4-39 shows the range of the Source CC pin voltage for a pull-up resistance to 3.3 V using the variance found in Table 4-27.</text>
