https://www.wch-ic.com/downloads/CH32V006DS0_PDF.html</text>
<text x="223.52" y="-58.42" size="1.778" layer="97" align="top-left">Table 3-16 General-purpose I/O static characteristics
        VIH: 0.3 x VDD + 0.7 to VDD
